(2), Adscreen Newlands 5 (20); SSRC 4 (17), Aberdeen 1 (5); Colinton
Castle 4 (18), Glasgow Accies 1 (5); Edinburgh Sports Club 2 (7),
Dunfermline 3 (14); Bridge of Allan 1 (5), Adscreen Newlands 4 (14).
</TEXT>
