<TEXT>
SALARIES of #80,000 a year plus performance-related bonuses are set to
be paid to the three new chief executives of the new Scottish water
authorities when they are appointed later this year, the Government said
last night.
Junior Scottish Office Minister George Kynoch disclosed the pay
arrangements for the heads of the new bodies for the North, West and
